  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42421875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtibvN8ehnUHibb52jjoViby70UXXvicoDCpECCpnh7kkl1QyFL8JV59zUnQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"245\" data-imgfileid=\"505177180\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f91e6370&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtibvN8ehnUHibb52jjoViby70UXXvicoDCpECCpnh7kkl1QyFL8JV59zUnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：定慧</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">芝加哥教授20分钟干完48小时工作，零基础小白10分钟造出完整App，前xAI工程师睡一觉醒来项目就做好了……Claude Code正在重新定义「编程」这件事。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:24px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">一个顶级程序员，30天没写一行代码。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">但他负责的项目，6个月做到了10亿美元年化营收！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&amp;mid=2652660003&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=da6f633164b1904b1a3a63da728af133&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"这不是科幻小说，这是Claude Code之父Boris Cherny的真实日常。\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">这不是科幻小说，这是Claude Code之父Boris Cherny的真实日常。</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">就在几天前，他在X上公开承认：过去30天，自己100%的代码都是Claude Code写的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">消息一出，整个AI社区炸锅了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49166666666666664\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"276\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=77d1a929&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtbEU9YOvrpDBicwvRzvVLSuDSCepUE5icib22bLMBWkog3Fic8jSMbZhvOQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">编程这件事，正在被彻底重新定义！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris Cherny是谁？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code项目的开发负责人，Anthropic的灵魂工程师之一。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">他曾被Cursor开发商Anysphere重金挖走，又被Anthropic闪电速度抢回来。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:center;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk0pafiv1ucd\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.330518697225573\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"829\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;background-color: transparent;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"254\" data-backh=\"338\" data-imgfileid=\"505177161\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ef79080&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtAJUk33y4c9suae9gLtBDJRyiawpCEUY5diaoBL9NibNFTBW4qlHsbrxcA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">可以说，他本人就是AI编程领域最顶尖的开发者之一。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">但就是这样一个人，现在完全不写代码了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">不是因为懒，而是因为Claude Code太强了！强到他认为自己手写代码反而是在浪费时间。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这意味着什么？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">编程，正在从「人写代码」变成「人指挥</span></strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">AI</span></strong><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">写代码」。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:center;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk0pao63dnd\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1342155009451795\" data-w=\"1058\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 79%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"637\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dc01e9cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtAtERImJsdlpMtnfndEXyj7UeJ2eSlOb4rwAJndlYJ5y8HVYRcvjriaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，你还在为学不会编程发愁吗？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">别急，2026年，这事儿可能真的不重要了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">就在这几天，一位完全不懂代码的博主在X上发帖：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">「Claude Code太TM疯狂了。我对编程一窍不通，完全是零基础。结果我刚用它10分钟，就做出了一个完整的Web应用——追踪迈阿密最佳日出观赏时间。」</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">10分钟，一个功能完整、界面精美的天气追踪App，从无到有。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.700925925925926\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"394\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8226eed2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtaYeD3MkicfA0rEibz4rUj9XwGsWgCz9I7hgwTdPY539fib6HnKicewIicfw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这还不是个例。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">24-48小时的活儿，20分钟干完</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">同一时间，芝加哥大学教授Alex Imas也在X上发出惊叹：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">「Claude Code简直疯了。我经常处理实验数据，原本需要24-48小时的工作量，它20分钟就搞定了。」</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">他的使用方式简单到令人发指：就是纯文本对话！</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk0lqru31h0o\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-data-temp-type=\"image\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgupspcrwi8\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;width: 100%;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: right;margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;width: 100%;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <div style=\"padding: 3px;box-sizing: border-box;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n           <div style=\"padding-top:5px;display:inline-block;width:100%;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:5px;box-sizing:border-box;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       