         <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n                   <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8194444444444444\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ddb360c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqt6PoD9vJ7X3avAsNT4IZpd3gpicBiavEIyXic4Zcx7jFraibkWmosKuT8Cg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n                  </div>\n                 </div>\n                </div>\n               </div>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"margin: 8px 0% 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54);box-sizing: border-box;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0pb5k7dpw\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk0pb5kcu5\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">左右滑动查看</span></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">比如他说：「找到数据文件experiment.csv，定位以下变量」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">然后Claude Code自动完成了以下全部步骤：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 在原始Qualtrics文件中找到相关变量</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 创建一个干净的CSV文件</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 写代码、建表格，做四种分析，还用LaTeX写好结果摘要</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">4. 用聚类分析找出数据里的「类型」，画出雷达图</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">5. 模拟不同类型在市场中的交互行为，输出可视化图表</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">所有代码透明可复现，所有文件本地保存，随时可以审查验证。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这位天天跟数据打交道的顶级教授说：这几个月，Claude Code彻底重塑了他的工作方式。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 48px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"309\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a0f23eb7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtbe3sjRwyxM1PMKdZnjM2icqzjMuhPjdibcS3AakK11ibdHUZ18ibxdicLpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">睡一觉醒来，App就做好了</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">如果说上面的案例还需要「懂点数据」，那这位前xAI工程师的玩法，直接把AI编程拉到了「全自动流水线」级别。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">Benjamin De Kraker（前xAI员工）分享了他搭建的「AI工厂」——一套用Claude Code agents打造的自动化系统：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">「我建了一个AI工厂，用Claude Code代理在我睡觉时帮我做App。」</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">这是什么概念？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8907407407407407\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"501\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c4b9b48b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtY9Ys8N1oo8iakoeoPoiaczRqeblqaeCKibaX28CQl9JicXBADV47OyYWKA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">他的系统由Claude Opus 4.5驱动，项目像工厂流水线一样从「想法」阶段流转到「调研」、「架构」、「编码」、「测试」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">工厂里的AI工人会做什么？</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 0.5em 25px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从市场调研开始，搜索网页和社交媒体</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">验证想法，检查应用商店的竞争情况，甚至自动注册域名</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">自动生成多轮UI设计稿</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23966065747614\" data-w=\"943\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"135\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=63d980ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtw6gCMCUyxlQg5oLg78hdBpawY9aFKGTKkbW5ukw9FtPWdExVsic52Dw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">然后呢？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">Benjamin早上醒来，项目就在那儿等着他review了：这个设计OK，那个需要改进，反馈完继续让AI干。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">整个过程有「工单文档」跟着项目走，就像真正的工厂生产线。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">一个人，顶一个团队。睡一觉的功夫，产品初版就出来了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 48px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\">简直离谱，真的是一人顶一万人。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px; text-align: justify; c